# Stack
Use Next.js App Router
Use TypeScript
Use Tailwind CSS for styling

# UI Components
Use shadcn/ui components for all UI
Import UI components from @/components/ui
Do not introduce other UI libraries
Prefer using existing components before creating custom ones

# UX / Interactions 
Follow ux best practices 

# Code Style
Prefer functional React components
Write readable, simple, maintainable code
Add comments only for complex logic
Avoid unnecessary abstractions or over-engineering

# File Organization
Follow standard Next.js file structure:
- pages or app directory for routes
- components for reusable UI
- hooks for custom hooks
- utils for helper functions

# API & Backend
Use Next.js API routes where applicable
Keep API logic clean and modular
Do not mix backend frameworks

# Best Practices
Follow consistent naming conventions
Keep components small and focused
Reuse components wherever possible